’Щ@ff5181926f3b5e4b866e1ad7525e47239282ce3c631814487e82261fea552998ЪcTitle: title: str capitalize
Path: Examples
Content:
Capitalize contents.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 'good day' | str capitalize
Good day

```
Capitalize contents.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 'anton' | str capitalize
Anton

```
Capitalize a column in a table.
